3. cs.COMM (Communication) - The paper discusses the challenges of supporting low-power, low-cost, and numerous devices, which are related to communication. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper discusses the cognitive radio concept, which is a system that can adapt to changing environments. 
5. cs.AR (Hardware Architecture) - The paper briefly mentions power and cost challenges, which are related to hardware architecture.
